\u02bboni: Hoʻololi i ke kūlana o kahi mea i ka manawa
ka wikiwiki: Ka māmā holo a me ke kuhikuhi o kekahi mea
ikaika: Paʻi a huki paha i ka neʻe a hoʻololi paha i ka neʻe o kekahi mea
inertia: ʻO ka manaʻo o kahi mea e pale aku i nā loli o ka neʻe
ka manawa: Huahana o ka nuipa a me ka wikiwiki o kekahi mea
umekaumaha: ʻO ka ikaika e huki ai i nā mea me ka nuipaʻa i kekahi i kekahi
kaumaha: ʻO ka ikaika i hana ʻia ma luna o kekahi mea ma muli o ka ʻumekaumaha
nuipa\u02bba: Ka nui o ka mea i loko o kekahi mea
m\u0101noanoa: ʻO ka nui o kēlā me kēia ʻāpana leo o kekahi mea
hana: Ka hoʻololi ʻana o ka ikehu ke hana ka ikaika a hoʻoneʻe i kekahi mea
ikehu kinetic: Ike o kekahi mea ma muli o kona neʻe ʻana
ikehu hiki: Hiki ke mālama ʻia ka ikehu ma muli o ke kūlana a i ʻole ka hoʻonohonoho ʻana o kekahi mea
mana: Ka helu i ka hana ʻana
paio: ʻO ka ikaika e kū'ē ana i ka neʻe ma waena o ʻelua mau ʻili e pili ana
kaomi: Hoʻoikaika ʻia i kēlā me kēia ʻāpana ʻāpana
lewa: Papahana kinoea a puni ka Honua
\u02bbolu\u02bbolu: ʻO ka ikaika i luna ma luna o kahi mea i hoʻopaʻa ʻia i loko o ka wai
kani: Ke ʻano o ka ikehu e holo ana ma ke ʻano he hawewe ma waena o kahi ʻano
